summary:
I\'ve made it so three floating cabbage plants are now part of the ground.
2 cabbage plants outside of Whiterun
1 Cabage plant outside of Loreius Farm

[u][center][size=5][color=Gold]Description[/color][/size][/center][/u] 
[center]I\'ve made it so three floating cabbage plants are now part of the ground.
2 cabbage plants outside of Whiterun
1 Cabage plant outside of Loreius Farm
If you see any floating cabbage plants like in the pictures let me know and I\'ll fix it.[/center] 
[line]

[center]1.2
Added cabbage at Loreius Farm.
Changed name to Floating Cabbage fix.
1.1
Remade the mod to remove the moved farmhouse. the mod is now clean.
1.0
Initial upload. [/center]
